<br>
Old Dirt:<br>
With the old dirty tricks, you would throw your dirt on 1 attacker (pray it stuck) and attack a 2nd attacker. This meant that even if the 1st attacker got behind you, he would fumble. The overall objective was to deal with 1 attacker at a time. When dirt stuck it worked very well. Problem was that it was purgable and was resisted alot. The 30 minute timer was awful too. This could also be done at range so you could pick your targets as you charged.<br>
<br>
New Dirt:<br>
<br>
The new dirt works on 2 different factors, having the dirt proc on the enemy and then the enemies chance of fumbling being 35%.  Also the dirt only lasts for 10 seconds so you have to keep on hitting the enemy to reapply it. On 1 vs 1's this works well as they can't really purge it and if its resisted once, then chances are they will fumble the next time.  The new timer is better too. The problem now is that it doesn't work well in taking 1 attacker out of the equation. You constantly have to keep switching attackers to reapply the dirt. This makes fighting very messy since F8 doesn't always work with many enemies around and targeting people that layer is hard (e.g. 2 lurikeens on top of each other). Its no longer a fire and forget kind of fighting.  Its almost impossible to tell who has the effect as well as the dirt wind sound will go off even if the person resists. <br>
<br>
Edit: Forgot 1 thing.  DW only works on melee. Triple Wield and Veno work on all classes. DW should work in some kind of fashion for casters.  <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=fester@lighttanksofdaoc>Fester</A> at: 6/23/03 6:01 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=uhno>uhno</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.grumbled.com/images/paradoxicon.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 51<br> <font color=#000000>(6/23/03 4:46 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm2.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=262.topic&index=6>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Dirty tricks change</span><hr size=1> As mentioned already.<br>
